data.description: OPEN HOUSE 4/11, Sunday 1:00-2:30. Welcome to 11585 W. Brady Road, Chesaning Township.  Renovated triplex on .36 acre, 3 bedroom 1 full bath with a deep jet tub. Main level laundry, large living room, kitchen & family room. Main level bedroom, 2 upper level bedrooms with built in closets. L-shaped enclosed front porch, 2 car detached garage.  She Shed/Man Cave in back of property. New kitchen appliances included.
